snippet.title: Radha Soami Satsang Beas - Official
snippet.description:
Radha Soami Satsang Beas (RSSB) along with its international affiliates is a religious organization guided by the fundamental spiritual beliefs found at the heart of most religions, under the mentorship of a living spiritual teacher.

There are a number of other contemporary movements that use the name ‘Radha Soami’ but Radha Soami Satsang Beas is not associated with any of them. There are also many imitators and imposters, particularly on the internet, who try to pass themselves off as “official RSSB” by using our name, our logo, copying our audio and video recordings, and even calling themselves RSSB. This YouTube Channel and its contents is the only official RSSB YouTube Channel. Our website http://www.rssb.org is the only official website for Radha Soami Satsang Beas.
